{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"56d3a871-764a-460d-ab28-71ed8f57ce98","content":"Yes, you'll hit compatibility issues. Here's the breakdown:\n\n**Target Framework Problems:**\n\n| Framework | MSTest v3 Support |\n|---|---|\n| `net462` | ✅ Supported |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | ❌ Dropped — MSTest v3 requires .NET 6.0+ for .NET Core |\n| `net5.0` | ❌ Dropped — .NET 5 is out of support |\n\nMSTest v3 only supports **.NET Framework ≥ 4.6.2** and **.NET ≥ 6.0**. You'll need to update `netcoreapp3.1` and `net5.0` to at least `net6.0` (or ideally `net8.0`).\n\n**Package Change:**\nMSTest v3 also ships a unified `MSTest` meta-package that replaces both `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter`. The recommended migration is:\n\n```xml\n<PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"3.x.x\" />\n```\n\nWould you like me to update the project file for the migration?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"8c0fe3e1-7ea4-4b13-a3c3-70022f332167","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The project targets `net5.0`, `net462`, and `netcoreapp3.1`. The user wants to migrate to MSTest v3. Let me think about what compatibility issues they might face.\n\nMSTest v3 (the MSTest.TestFramework 3.x / MSTest.TestAdapter 3.x packages, or the unified `MSTest` meta-package) dropped support for older target frameworks. Specifically:\n\n- MSTest v3 requires at minimum .NET Framework 4.6.2 and .NET 6.0+.\n- `net5.0` is no longer supported — it's out of support and MSTest v3 dropped it.\n\n\n- `netcoreapp3.1` is also no longer supported — MSTest v3 dropped it.\n- `net462` should still be supported (it's .NET Framework 4.6.2).\n\nSo the user will run into compatibility issues with `net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1` target frameworks. MSTest v3 also introduced a unified `MSTest` package that replaces both `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter`, which is the recommended approach for v3.","outputTokens":573,"requestId":"67C2:13C959:2F29130:345E98C:69FD5066"},"id":"637d77ff-d435-4dc8-ad10-4d6eef29a205","timestamp":"2026-05-08T02:54:40.904Z","parentId":"06fdcf08-a600-4a96-9ad8-822a6269fdda"}
